BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260509T063600
DTEND:20260509T163000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.938ft at 06:36\n-2.969ft at 16:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 <strong>Dawn to 10:00AM:</strong> Mainly old swell for thigh-waist high su
 rf in the morning. Winds are light/variable\, while the tide backs out to 
 a draining late AM low. \n\n<strong>Afternoon Outlook:</strong>  Some new 
 WNW/NW swell and SSW Southern Hemi joins in during the afternoon\, for mor
 e waist-stomach high waves. Gentle S wind develops back half of the day fo
 r a little texture.  Late afternoon high tide slows tide sensitive breaks.
  
END:VEVENT
